[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     76[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Coordination conversation logs include data spanning multiple
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     77[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # organizations, multiple pharmacies, multiple ancillary
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     78[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # services, and one or more caregivers. The data is dense PHI
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     79[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # with cross-organizational sharing implications. Log
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     80[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # structural metadata only (session_id, patient_id_hash,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     81[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # speaker_role, intent, tool name, tool latency, tool outcome,
