[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     84[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # arguments that contain identifiers, never specific
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     85[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # medication entries or clinician names. Full transcripts and
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     86[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # full tool calls live in the audit pipeline (Firehose plus
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     87[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Object-Lock S3) with state-specific medical-record retention
