[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1677[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             parsed)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1678[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1679[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Step 2D: enforce per-source consent posture.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1680[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # If the patient has not consented to ingestion from
