[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1726[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Step 2F: normalize to the coordination-state
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1727[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # schema. For FHIR-native sources the data lands in
