[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2704[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     ):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2705[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         return (
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2706[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             f"You are {INSTITUTION_DISPLAY_NAME}'s care "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2707[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             "coordination assistant. You are a chat tool, "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2708[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             "not a person and not a clinician. You track "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2709[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             "and surface; clinicians decide. You are "
