[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3508[0m:[38;5;10m[49m What can go wrong if you skip or shortcut this: the discharge-to-home gap (the 48-hour-to-72-hour window where most preventable readmissions originate) is unmanaged, medication reconciliation is left to chance, follow-up appointments are not validated against the protocol window, red-flag warnings are not delivered, and the transition closure is silent.
