[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3523[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3524[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         Step 8: track referral lifecycles to closure.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3525[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         Returns a structured result describing the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3526[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         transition outcome. Production has each referral
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3527[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         state machine validate transitions against the
