[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3532[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Valid values: ordered, communicated, scheduled,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3533[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # rescheduled, attended, no_showed, cancelled,
