[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3709[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         reconciliation result and any seams raised.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3710[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3711[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Step 9A: classify the source.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3712[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         source_type = medication_event.get("source_type")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3713[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3714[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Step 9B: normalize the medication entry.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    3715[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         # Production canonicalizes drug name (RxNorm),
